1.content: Date of post 1/1/2001 . Intro Paragraph: alskdj;lkjf;lkj;lkajs;ldkj;lkjaf . And that is why you should keep reading . I wanted this or thought I did, but getting there was another matter . It stared with a conversation and some thinking about layout. Shiny new PCBs full of rookie mistakes but I was proud all the same . In the end I got my first batch of boards built and was motivated to do it again, but better.
